text:
Our beautiful national forests are a district staple, and I'm committed to protecting them. That's why I organized a roundtable discussion with forestry managers from the @forestservice across the third district to ensure they have the resources to do their jobs. 

The foresters reported they're well-staffed for fire prevention efforts and, encouragingly, have recently seen an increase in staffing thanks to the pay increase for federal wildland firefighters that I helped pass last year. 

